      "content": "i mean \"polished\" vs \"energetic\"... isn't that just a polite way of saying uws is for rich white people and harlem is where the crime/unpredictability is? like if i'm a solo traveler, wouldn't i just assume harlem is more dangerous or \"sketchy\" based on how people usually talk about it?",
